Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.map

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Cell
    Abstract class that represents the abstract object which composes the board game and which is developed deeper by the Block class
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Block
    Class that represents a block, the concrete object described by the cell
    Board
    Class that represents a board, which contains 25 cells in a 5x5 map
    Pawn
    Abstract class that represents a generic pawn, giving indication for how any object (different from a block) can behave on the board.
    Worker
    Class that represents the pawn "worker" It contains its previous cell, previous build, gender and id
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Level
    Enumeration that represents the level of the cell
